                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6365" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0999</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8501 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">是四两拨千斤还是城头变换大王旗？天山股份再演A股千亿并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is it Moving Mountains with Few Resources or the Old Wine in a New Bottle? Xinjiang Tianshan Cement Co., Ltd. Conducted $100 Billion M&amp;A Restructuring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱卫林，江园园</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆天山水泥股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购方式；资产重组；对赌协议</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M&amp;A method; asset restructuring;Valuation Adjustment Mechanism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要介绍了新疆天山水泥股份有限公司（以下简称“天山股份”）通过发行股份等方式收购中国建材股份有限公司（以下简称“中国建材”）水泥板块资产的并购重组过程。近年来受供给侧改革及“双碳”政策的影响，淘汰落后产能，发展绿色环保产能，解决产能过剩也成为水泥行业的近些年改革的重点。2020年8月天山股份发布此次并购重组公告预案，表明此次并购重组的对象为中国建材旗下的水泥板块，该公司希望通过此次并购能够实现资源优势配置的同时解决行业产能过剩问题。通过耗时大约一年的并购重组过程，天山股份最终实现了成为行业内体量最大的水泥企业，同时中国建材也实现了水泥板块的有效整合。本案例可以帮助学生理解通过发行股票及支付现金方式并购资产的过程，了解上市公司并购重组的相关概念以及如何降低并购重组后产生的风险，对于水泥企业通过市场并购的方式，利用资本扩大市场具有较大的参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case mainly introduces the process of tianshan shares acquiring assets in China National Building Materials cement sector through the issuance of shares. In recent years, affected by supply-side reforms, the elimination of backward production capacity, the development of green and environmental protection production capacity, and the solution of overcapacity have also become the focus of reform in the cement industry in recent years. In August 2020，Tianshan Co., Ltd. released the preliminary announcement of the merger and reorganization, indicating that the object of the merger and reorganization was the cement sector under China National Building Materials, and the company hoped that through this merger and acquisition, it could achieve the allocation of resource advantages and solve the overcapacity of the industry. Through the M&amp;A and restructuring process that took about a year, Tianshan co., Ltd. finally achieved the largest cement enterprise in the industry, and China National Building Materials achieved effective integration of the cement sector. This case can help students understand the process of acquiring assets by issuing shares and paying cash, which is of great reference value for cement companies to use capital equity to expand the market and establish a strategic defense line through market mergers and acquisitions. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购的动因、同一控制下的并购重组；并购重组的类型、并购资产的支付方式；补偿协议的作用；并购重组后的协同效应；并购重组后的风险及防范措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
